Name: Search in File

Implementation :
Assembly 8086 language 

Purpose: 
The program should take as input a string to search for, and search option (Case Match: ON/OFF ,Whole Word: ON/OFF ) and a file path. Then it outputs a list stating the line where this pattern was found, and displaying this line. If the file is not found an error message should be displayed.

Algorithm:

Input: 
A string to search for, search option (Case Match: ON/OFF, Whole Word: ON/OFF), and a file path.
Register usage within the routine: 

Output: 
Number of the line in the text file and display the line.
Error; if the file is not found.

Note:
You must apply the case match and whole word option .
